<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6644791>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Meschia brevirostris sp. nov., paratype, female, ventral view (A), holotype, male, head, dorsal (B) and ventral (C) views, B & C, same scale, paratype, male, metathoracic scent gland in light microscopy (D) and SEM (E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6644791/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6644787>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Meschia brevirostris sp. nov., paratypes: female, dorsal views of light (A) and dark (B) colour form." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6644787/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6644799>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Meschia brevirostris sp. nov., female, abdomen, ventral view (A); B–E, male genitalia: pygophore, dorsal view (B), aedeagus, dorsal view (C, D), left paramere, dorsal (upper) view (E). Abbreviations: ba, basal apparatus; bl, blade; c, conjunctiva; cs, cuplike sclerite; dl, dorsal lobe of paramere; ds, ductus seminis; ej, ejaculatory reservoir; gp, gonoporal process; hp, helicoid process; id, indentation; lm, lateral magin of pygophore opening; mcp, median conical protuberance; ml, membranous lobe; ph, phallotheca; sg, secondary gonopore; sm, spermatheca; sp II–VII, spiracles on sterna II-VII; w, wing; ve, vesica; vl, ventral lobe of paramere." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6644799/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6644797>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Meschia brevirostris sp. nov., distal area of labium (A), mesotarsus (B), distal area of tarsus showing claw and associated structures (C), male, trichobothrial pattern on right side of posterior abdominal segments (D), submedial trichobothria on abdominal sternum IV (E), trichobothrial distribution pattern in male (left) and female (right) (F), trichobothria on abdominal sternum VII (G), enlarged structure of trichobothria on abdominal sterna III and IV (H, I)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6644797/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6644793>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Meschia brevirostris sp. nov., paratype, male, ventral view (A) and paratype, female, dorsal view (B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6644793/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6644805>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Meschia brevirostris sp. nov., distribution in New Caledonia: Aoupinié (1), Col d’Amieu and Farino env. rain forest (2)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6644805/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6644801>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Meschia brevirostris sp. nov., collection site, Col d'Amieu, 13–17.03.2008 (A, B), night collection with light traps, 17.03.2008 (C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6644801/files/figure.png" ;
